videos.description: Kansas big man Udoka Azubuike goes up to block a shot then comes down holding his ankle.
videos.headline: Azubuike helped off the court

videos.description: Kansas center David McCormack can't control the pass but recovers and lays it in.
videos.headline: Kansas' McCormack bobbles pass then scores

videos.description: Kansas' Dedric Lawson makes the sweet layup then gets a steal which leads to a Devon Dotson corner 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Kansas goes on a mini run with layup and 3-pointer

videos.description: Devon Dotson gets the steal, spins away from the defender then throws the lob to Quentin Grimes who lays it in.
videos.headline: Kansas gets out in transition and scores

videos.description: Quentin Grimes catches the lob from Marcus Garrett and finishes with the two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Grimes flies high for alley-oop dunk
